name: Adam M Presents: The Mighty M - The Album
description:
Adam M Presents his brand new double CD album - The Mighty M. 

The album consists of 2 discs catering for both clubbers & DJ's. Disc 1 is mixed by Adam M & contains exclusive tracks forthcoming on Hi Oktane records as well as 11 brand new collaborations & Remixes from Adam M & Co. 

On Disc 2 there are 10 DJ friendly single tracks from Adam M & friends such as Farley, Maddox, Guyver, Ben Stevens & Dave Owens to name just a few...
